### Personal Finance Application - API Testing

### 1. User Registration
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "firstName": "Test",
  "lastName": "User"
}

### 2. User Login (Demo User)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "usernameOrEmail": "demo",
  "password": "password123"
}

> {%
client.global.set("jwt_token", response.body.token);
%}

### 3. Get Current User Profile
GET http://localhost:8080/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 4. Get Dashboard Overview
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 5. Get Financial Insights
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/insights
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 6. Get Monthly Trends
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/monthly-trends?monthsBack=6
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 7. Get All Income
GET http://localhost:8080/api/income
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 8. Add New Income
POST http://localhost:8080/api/income
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Consulting Work",
  "amount": 2000.00,
  "category": "FREELANCE",
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "isRecurring": false,
  "notes": "One-time consulting project"
}

### 9. Get Income Categories
GET http://localhost:8080/api/income/categories
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 10. Get Income by Category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/income/by-category?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 11. Get All Expenses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 12. Add New Expense
POST http://localhost:8080/api/expenses
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Restaurant Dinner",
  "amount": 85.50,
  "category": "FOOD",
  "date": "2024-01-15",
  "notes": "Dinner with friends"
}

### 13. Get Expenses by Category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/by-category?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 14. Get Recent Expenses
GET http://localhost:8080/api/expenses/recent?limit=5
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 15. Get All Goals
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goals
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 16. Create New Goal
POST http://localhost:8080/api/goals
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Home Down Payment",
  "description": "Save for a house down payment",
  "targetAmount": 50000.00,
  "currentAmount": 5000.00,
  "targetDate": "2025-06-01",
  "priority": "HIGH"
}

### 17. Get Active Goals
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goals/active
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 18. Update Goal Progress (replace {goalId} with actual ID)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/goals/1/add-progress
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 500.00
}

### 19. Get Goal Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/goals/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 20. Get Investment Capacity
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments/capacity
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 21. Get Investment Recommendations (Conservative)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments/recommendations?riskProfile=CONSERVATIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 22. Get Investment Recommendations (Moderate)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments/recommendations?riskProfile=MODERATE
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 23. Get Investment Recommendations (Aggressive)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments/recommendations?riskProfile=AGGRESSIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 24. Get Risk Profiles Information
GET http://localhost:8080/api/investments/risk-profiles
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### 25. Get Spending Analysis
GET http://localhost:8080/api/dashboard/spending-analysis?startDate=2024-01-01&endDate=2024-01-31
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

###
